{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":813,"text":"So, I thought a lot about\nthe first word I'd say today,"},{"time":3641,"text":"and I decided to say \"Colombia.\""},{"time":6155,"text":"And the reason, I don't know\nhow many of you have visited Colombia,"},{"time":10214,"text":"but Colombia is just north\nof the border with Brazil."},{"time":13064,"text":"It's a beautiful country"},{"time":14271,"text":"with extraordinary people,\nlike me and others -- (Laughter) --"},{"time":17727,"text":"and it's populated\nwith incredible fauna, flora."},{"time":23157,"text":"It's got water; it's got everything\nto be the perfect place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27324,"text":"But we have a few problems."},{"time":29052,"text":"You may have heard of some of them."},{"time":30722,"text":"We have the oldest\nstanding guerrilla in the world."},{"time":34415,"text":"It's been around for over 50 years,"},{"time":36414,"text":"which means that in my lifetime,"},{"time":39177,"text":"I have never lived one day \nof peace in my country."},{"time":43852,"text":"This guerrilla -- and the main group\nis the FARC guerrillas,"},{"time":47725,"text":"Revolutionary Armed Forces of Colombia --"},{"time":50142,"text":"they have financed their war\nby kidnapping, by extortion,"},{"time":57631,"text":"by getting into the drug trade,\nby illegal mining."},{"time":61480,"text":"There has been terrorism.\nThere have been random bombs."},{"time":65301,"text":"So it's not good.\nIt's not really good."},{"time":69576,"text":"And if you look at the human cost\nof this war over 50 years,"},{"time":74376,"text":"we have had more than\n5.7 million displaced population."},{"time":79197,"text":"It's one of the biggest displaced\npopulations in the world,"},{"time":82265,"text":"and this conflict has cost\nover 220,000 lives."},{"time":86374,"text":"So it's a little bit like\nthe Bol√≠var wars again."},{"time":89432,"text":"It's a lot of people who\nhave died unnecessarily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92587,"text":"We are now in the middle of peace talks,"},{"time":95665,"text":"and we've been trying to help\nresolve this problem peacefully,"},{"time":98958,"text":"and as part of that,"},{"time":100518,"text":"we decided to try something\ncompletely lateral and different:"},{"time":104427,"text":"Christmas lights."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106471,"text":"So Christmas lights, and you're saying,"},{"time":108977,"text":"what the hell is this guy\ngoing to talk about?"},{"time":112173,"text":"I am going to talk about gigantic trees"},{"time":116785,"text":"that we put in nine strategic \npathways in the jungle"},{"time":122412,"text":"covered with Christmas lights."},{"time":124421,"text":"These trees helped us \ndemobilize 331 guerrillas,"},{"time":130599,"text":"roughly five percent\nof the guerrilla force at the time."},{"time":135097,"text":"These trees were lit up at night,"},{"time":137675,"text":"and they had a sign beside them"},{"time":140044,"text":"that said, \"If Christmas can come\nto the jungle, you can come home."},{"time":144735,"text":"Demobilize."},{"time":146435,"text":"At Christmas, everything is possible.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":148916,"text":"So how do we know these trees worked?"},{"time":152209,"text":"Well, we got 331, which is okay,"},{"time":154215,"text":"but we also know that\nnot a lot of guerrillas saw them,"},{"time":159480,"text":"but we know that a lot of\nguerrillas heard about them,"},{"time":161984,"text":"and we know this"},{"time":163191,"text":"because we are constantly talking\nto demobilized guerrillas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166295,"text":"So let me take you back\nfour years before the trees."},{"time":169050,"text":"Four years before the trees,\nwe were approached by the government"},{"time":172735,"text":"to help them come up with\na communications strategy"},{"time":176882,"text":"to get as many guerrillas\nas we could out of the jungle."},{"time":180082,"text":"The government had a military strategy,"},{"time":182534,"text":"it had a legal strategy,"},{"time":183862,"text":"it had a political strategy, but it said,"},{"time":186691,"text":"\"We don't really have\na communications strategy,"},{"time":189036,"text":"and it probably would be\na good thing to have,\""},{"time":191987,"text":"so we decided to\nimmediately jump into this,"},{"time":196373,"text":"because it is an opportunity\nto affect the outcome of the conflict"},{"time":201588,"text":"with the things that we do,\nwith the tools that we have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206264,"text":"But we didn't know very much about it."},{"time":208493,"text":"We didn't understand in Colombia, \nif you live in the cities,"},{"time":211709,"text":"you're very far away from where \nthe war is actually happening,"},{"time":214803,"text":"so you don't really understand it,"},{"time":216816,"text":"and we asked the government \nto give us access"},{"time":218982,"text":"to as many demobilized\nguerrillas as possible."},{"time":221524,"text":"And we talked to about 60 of them"},{"time":223980,"text":"before we felt we fully\nunderstood the problem."},{"time":229074,"text":"We talked about -- they told us why \nthey had joined the guerrillas,"},{"time":232386,"text":"why the left the guerrillas,\nwhat their dreams were,"},{"time":235025,"text":"what their frustrations were,"},{"time":236713,"text":"and from those conversations\ncame the underlying insight"},{"time":241173,"text":"that has guided this whole campaign,"},{"time":243670,"text":"which is that guerrillas are as much\nprisoners of their organizations"},{"time":249060,"text":"as the people they hold hostage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251533,"text":"And at the beginning, we were\nso touched by these stories,"},{"time":254313,"text":"we were so amazed by these stories,"},{"time":256596,"text":"that we thought that maybe \nthe best way to talk to the guerrillas"},{"time":259735,"text":"was to have them talk to themselves,"},{"time":262570,"text":"so we recorded about a hundred\ndifferent stories during the first year,"},{"time":267354,"text":"and we put them on\nthe radio and television"},{"time":269722,"text":"so that the guerrillas in the jungle\ncould hear stories, their stories,"},{"time":274067,"text":"or stories similar to theirs,"},{"time":276415,"text":"and when they heard them,\nthey decided to go out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279195,"text":"I want to tell you one of these stories."},{"time":281789,"text":"This person you see here \nis Giovanni Andres."},{"time":284443,"text":"Giovanni Andres is 25\nwhen we took that picture."},{"time":287274,"text":"He had been seven years in the guerrilla,\nand he had demobilized very recently."},{"time":291963,"text":"His story is the following:"},{"time":294528,"text":"He was recruited when he was 17,"},{"time":297724,"text":"and sometime later,\nin his squadron, if you will,"},{"time":302909,"text":"this beautiful girl was recruited,\nand they fell in love."},{"time":308085,"text":"Their conversations were about\nwhat their family was going to be like,"},{"time":311957,"text":"what their kids' names would be,"},{"time":314288,"text":"how their life would be\nwhen they left the guerrilla."},{"time":316885,"text":"But it turns out"},{"time":318342,"text":"that love is very strictly forbidden\nin the lower ranks of the guerrilla,"},{"time":321935,"text":"so their romance was discovered\nand they were separated."},{"time":325298,"text":"He was sent very far away,\nand she was left behind."},{"time":328711,"text":"She was very familiar with the territory,"},{"time":331368,"text":"so one night, when she was on guard,"},{"time":333949,"text":"she just left,"},{"time":335650,"text":"and she went to the army, she demobilized,"},{"time":339112,"text":"and she was one of the persons\nthat we had the fortune to talk to,"},{"time":342996,"text":"and we were really touched by this story,"},{"time":345346,"text":"so we made a radio spot,"},{"time":347714,"text":"and it turns out, by chance,"},{"time":350640,"text":"that far away, many, \nmany kilometers north,"},{"time":354123,"text":"he heard her on the radio,"},{"time":357281,"text":"and when he heard her on the radio,\nhe said, \"What am I doing here?"},{"time":361851,"text":"She had the balls to get out.\nI need to do the same thing.\""},{"time":367293,"text":"And he did."},{"time":368691,"text":"He walked for two days and two nights,"},{"time":371589,"text":"and he risked his life and he got out,"},{"time":373952,"text":"and the only thing\nhe wanted was to see her."},{"time":376913,"text":"The only thing that was\nin his mind was to see her."},{"time":380439,"text":"The story was, they did meet."},{"time":383356,"text":"I know you're wondering if they did meet."},{"time":385887,"text":"They did meet."},{"time":387136,"text":"She had been recruited when she was 15,\nand she left when she was 17,"},{"time":391139,"text":"so there were a lot\nof other complications,"},{"time":393199,"text":"but they did eventually meet."},{"time":394931,"text":"I don't know if they're together now,\nbut I can find out. (Laughter)"},{"time":400206,"text":"But what I can tell you is that\nour radio strategy was working."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408177,"text":"The problem is that it was working\nin the lower ranks of the guerrilla."},{"time":411861,"text":"It was not working with the commanders,"},{"time":414224,"text":"the people that are\nmore difficult to replace,"},{"time":416435,"text":"because you can easily recruit\nbut you can't get the older commanders."},{"time":422013,"text":"So we thought, well,\nwe'll use the same strategy."},{"time":425696,"text":"We'll have commanders\ntalking to commanders."},{"time":428262,"text":"And we even went as far\nas asking ex-commanders of the guerrilla"},{"time":432038,"text":"to fly on helicopters with microphones"},{"time":434773,"text":"telling the people that\nused to fight with them,"},{"time":438234,"text":"\"There is a better life out there,\""},{"time":440347,"text":"\"I'm doing good,\"\n\"This is not worth it,\" etc."},{"time":442924,"text":"But, as you can all imagine,\nit was very easy to counteract,"},{"time":448030,"text":"because what was\nthe guerrilla going to say?"},{"time":450583,"text":"\"Yeah, right, if he doesn't do that,\nhe's going to get killed.\""},{"time":453791,"text":"So it was easy, so we were\nsuddenly left with nothing,"},{"time":457856,"text":"because the guerrilla\nwere spreading the word"},{"time":460135,"text":"that all of those things are done"},{"time":462846,"text":"because if they don't do it, \nthey're in danger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468348,"text":"And somebody, some\nbrilliant person in our team,"},{"time":471512,"text":"came back and said,\n\"You know what I noticed?"},{"time":475150,"text":"I noticed that around Christmastime,"},{"time":478707,"text":"there have been peaks of demobilization"},{"time":481398,"text":"since this war has started.\""},{"time":484393,"text":"And that was incredible,"},{"time":487000,"text":"because that led us to think \nthat we needed to talk to the human being"},{"time":492481,"text":"and not to the soldier."},{"time":494052,"text":"We needed to step away from talking"},{"time":496189,"text":"from government to army,\nfrom army to army,"},{"time":501459,"text":"and we needed to talk\nabout the universal values,"},{"time":504756,"text":"and we needed to talk about humanity."},{"time":507218,"text":"And that was when\nthe Christmas tree happened."},{"time":510592,"text":"This picture that I have here,"},{"time":512599,"text":"you see this is the planning\nof the Christmas trees,"},{"time":515791,"text":"and that man you see there\nwith the three stars,"},{"time":519540,"text":"he's Captain Juan Manuel Valdez."},{"time":521669,"text":"Captain Valdez was the first \nhigh-ranking official"},{"time":526640,"text":"to give us the helicopters \nand the support we needed"},{"time":530503,"text":"to put these Christmas trees up,"},{"time":532853,"text":"and he said in that meeting\nsomething that I will never forget."},{"time":536145,"text":"He said, \"I want to do this\nbecause being generous makes me stronger,"},{"time":543339,"text":"makes my men feel stronger.\""},{"time":545691,"text":"And I get very emotional\nwhen I remember him"},{"time":548431,"text":"because he was killed later in combat\nand we really miss him,"},{"time":552816,"text":"but I wanted you all to see him,\nbecause he was really, really important."},{"time":559092,"text":"He gave us all the support\nto put up the first Christmas trees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563220,"text":"What happened later is that\nthe guerrillas who came out"},{"time":565953,"text":"during the Christmas tree \noperation and all of that"},{"time":569573,"text":"said, \"That's really good,\nChristmas trees are really cool,"},{"time":573369,"text":"but you know what?\nWe really don't walk anymore."},{"time":575899,"text":"We use rivers.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":577351,"text":"So rivers are the highways of the jungle,"},{"time":580738,"text":"and this is something we learned,"},{"time":582935,"text":"and most of the recruiting was being done\nin and around the river villages."},{"time":588237,"text":"So we went to these river villages,"},{"time":590520,"text":"and we asked the people,"},{"time":592421,"text":"and probably some of them were\ndirect acquaintances of the guerrillas."},{"time":595775,"text":"We asked them, \"Can you send\nguerrillas a message?\""},{"time":599769,"text":"We collected over 6,000 messages."},{"time":603159,"text":"Some of them were notes saying, get out."},{"time":605805,"text":"Some of them were toys.\nSome of them were candy."},{"time":608522,"text":"Even people took off their jewelry,\ntheir little crosses and religious things,"},{"time":612725,"text":"and put them in these floating balls\nthat we sent down the rivers"},{"time":618140,"text":"so that they could be picked up at night."},{"time":620735,"text":"And we sent thousands\nof these down the rivers,"},{"time":623093,"text":"and then picked them up\nlater if they weren't."},{"time":625263,"text":"But lots of them were picked up."},{"time":626795,"text":"This generated, on average,\na demobilization every six hours,"},{"time":631686,"text":"so this was incredible and it was about:\nCome home at Christmas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636920,"text":"Then came the peace process,"},{"time":641001,"text":"and when the peace process started,"},{"time":643442,"text":"the whole mindset\nof the guerrilla changed."},{"time":645762,"text":"And it changed because"},{"time":648087,"text":"it makes you think, \"Well,\nif there's a peace process,"},{"time":650836,"text":"this is probably going to be over."},{"time":652778,"text":"At some point I'm going to get out.\""},{"time":654890,"text":"And their fears completely changed,"},{"time":657096,"text":"and their fears were not about,\n\"Am I going to get killed?\""},{"time":660324,"text":"Their fears were, \"Am I\ngoing to be rejected?"},{"time":663923,"text":"When I get out of this,\nam I going to be rejected?\""},{"time":666732,"text":"So the past Christmas, \nwhat we did was we asked --"},{"time":669803,"text":"we found 27 mothers of guerrillas,"},{"time":673550,"text":"and we asked them to give us \npictures of their children,"},{"time":677784,"text":"when they only could recognize themselves,\nso as not to put their lives in danger,"},{"time":681989,"text":"and we asked them to give\nthe most motherly message you can get,"},{"time":686265,"text":"which is, \"Before you were a guerrilla,\nyou were my child,"},{"time":690857,"text":"so come home, I'm waiting for you.\""},{"time":693109,"text":"You can see the pictures here.\nI'll show you a couple."},{"time":696261,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":697605,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703552,"text":"And these pictures were placed\nin many different places,"},{"time":708730,"text":"and a lot of them came back,"},{"time":712892,"text":"and it was really, really beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715840,"text":"And then we decided to work with society."},{"time":719315,"text":"So we did mothers around Christmastime."},{"time":721972,"text":"Now let's talk about\nthe rest of the people."},{"time":724826,"text":"And you may be aware of this or not,\nbut there was a World Cup this year,"},{"time":730190,"text":"and Colombia played really well,\nand it was a unifying moment for Colombia."},{"time":737617,"text":"And what we did was tell the guerrillas,"},{"time":741453,"text":"\"Come, get out of the jungle.\nWe're saving a place for you.\""},{"time":745510,"text":"So this was television, this was \nall different types of media saying,"},{"time":750575,"text":"\"We are saving a place for you.\""},{"time":753037,"text":"The soldier here in the commercial says,"},{"time":756056,"text":"\"I'm saving a place for you\nright here in this helicopter"},{"time":758921,"text":"so that you can get out of this jungle\nand go enjoy the World Cup.\""},{"time":762734,"text":"Ex-football players, radio announcers,"},{"time":765901,"text":"everybody was saving\na place for the guerrilla."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768195,"text":"So since we started this work\na little over eight years ago,"},{"time":772970,"text":"17,000 guerrillas have demobilized."},{"time":776397,"text":"I do not -- (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":780436,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":783017,"text":"I don't want to say in any way\nthat it only has to do with what we do,"},{"time":791714,"text":"but what I do know is that our work\nand the work that we do"},{"time":798288,"text":"may have helped a lot of them\nstart thinking about demobilization,"},{"time":802960,"text":"and it may have helped a lot of them\ntake the final decision."},{"time":806968,"text":"If that is true, advertising is still\none of the most powerful tools of change"},{"time":813498,"text":"that we have available."},{"time":815740,"text":"And I speak not only my behalf,"},{"time":818631,"text":"but on behalf of all\nthe colleagues I see here"},{"time":820975,"text":"who work in advertising,"},{"time":822639,"text":"and of all the team that has\nworked with me to do this,"},{"time":826665,"text":"that if you want to change the world,"},{"time":829914,"text":"or if you want to achieve \npeace, please call us."},{"time":832375,"text":"We'd love to help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":833875,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835238,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}